## How to Run Demo

```bash
# 1. Start MongoDB
brew services start mongodb-community

# 2. Seed database (if not done)
cd packages/api && bun run seed

# 3. Start API (port 3001)
cd packages/api && bun run dev

# 4. Start Frontend (port 3000)
cd apps/web && pnpm dev

# 5. Open browser
open http://localhost:3000
```

---

## Demo Flow

1. **Dashboard** - Show fleet overview (128 trains, live data)
2. **Fleet** - Browse all trains, filter by type
3. **What-If** - Run optimization, show before/after
4. **Calendar** - View scheduled maintenance
5. **Export** - Download Excel report

